  ' ============================================================
  ' PROCESSES (LEGACY / OUTDATED)
  '
  ' NOTE: This block is superseded by sie-processes-v1.puml which contains
  ' the normative process definitions for SIE:
  ' - Systemic Emergence Management (EmergenceProcess, Observation, etc.)
  ' - Systemic Constraint Management (CoherenceCheckProcess, FeasibilityAssessment, etc.)
  '
  ' The definitions below are intentionally kept as historical reference.
  ' For normative process design, see:
  '   !include sie-processes-v1.puml
